{"tid":2403331,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅兵咸永道員工確診 中環太子大廈24樓即時消毒","createTime":"2021-02-11T04:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T07:16:23.000Z","uid":5195,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c6e65f1100e79409e5db831e255ddb29615b4c","tid":2403331,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"羅兵咸永道會計師事務所（PwC）表示，一名於太子大廈24樓工作的職員，2月10日確診新冠肺炎，最後返回公司日期是1月31日。PwC正跟患者緊密聯絡，盼了解患者的健康情況。<br />\n<br />\n公司已即時安排於涉事樓屠消毒，強調一直把員工的健康和安全放在首位，並採取了所有防護措施，確保工作環境安全。PwC呼籲同事在工作期間，要佩戴口罩及保持社交距離。"},{"pid":"c1c2c20ce65acdffd547714ebcbbec8727b4c638","tid":2403331,"uid":224533,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:45:03.000Z","msg":"封樓！封樓！封樓！<br />\n全幢強制驗毒啦"},{"pid":"5879f96a19866e93f487b537c54e5a9d08b18bd3","tid":2403331,"uid":196625,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"咁點OT好?"},{"pid":"8ea286a222eb9786b8200e05bf2f42fa8546c6ce","tid":2403331,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c1c2c20ce65acdffd547714ebcbbec8727b4c638","tid":2403331,"uid":224533,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:45:03.000Z","msg":"封樓！封樓！封樓！<br />\n全幢強制驗毒啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:45:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">強制年三十封到初一等結果<br />\n<br />\n</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ddd0f44d58be8141fc24881c4d11e60d95f533","tid":2403331,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1c2c20ce65acdffd547714ebcbbec8727b4c638","tid":2403331,"uid":224533,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:45:03.000Z","msg":"封樓！封樓！封樓！<br />\n全幢強制驗毒啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"